{
  "stem": "2004.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And whenever they have to go somewhere, they tried to go in a group-- safety in numbers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Now, I particular remember one incident where they went.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were sitting in a restaurant, in a Jewish-owned restaurant, a coffee shop so to say, and they were having their coffee or whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a group of Polish students, college students, came in and started making trouble.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the owner, who was Jewish, asked them politely to leave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they, of course, started a fight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Jewish group stood up and being-- they were actually attacked.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they actually gave them a-- a-- a little beating there that they'll never forget.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It just so happened that there was one particular young man who was quite muscular, quite strong.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I guess you would call him-- in this country, you would call him a typical football player.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he gave them a licking that they-- I don't think that they would ever come-- came back to that particular place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was quickly forgotten, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was sort of a satisfaction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After, after hearing stories whereby we were on the receiving end, it turned out that somebody else was on the receiving end this time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think they particularly-- to, to them, at least to the Polish population on the Polish side, the Polish Gentile population, the fact that we got along with the Jews-- it was just a natural because we were all Jews, so all the same type.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it really didn't matter to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We never really had any disagreements because we were all, of course, part of the same group, socioeconomic group, and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
